snippet.title: Nephenthesys - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Nephenthesys is an arcade top-down shoot 'em up action game developed by Let's Dev Studios and Eastasiasoft Limited. Players will pilot a ship of their choosing after encountering an unidentified object with absurd energy signatures. Recover the object with heavy opposition attempting to thwart the mission at hand. Blast through enemy ships, collect power-ups for wider shot spreads and special bombs, face off massive bosses, and more. Traverse through caverns, waterways, cityscapes, and other unique environments. Nephenthesys is launching on January 17 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch, and PC.
